latestIgtvVideos.title: Another on the spot!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
This was the platform where i started my dance when i was jst 3. I worship this platform. So this year after 2 years i stood up there. This one was on the spot. I was just talking with @nidhi_guravv and @_nusta.confused_  and suddenly @yadneshzam announced on mic like "ata tumchya mukar yeta Karishma Zambaulikar". I got stuck for second and @_nusta.confused_ this boy threw me on the stage 😂 Then asked which song.. i told konsa bhi chalega.. tbh i never heard jugnu song before.. i mean full song.. i was used to only small part of it as a reel.. bt then i tried my best.. i was injured some moments before that's y couldn't control on my footsteps.. Bt m satisfied with it... 

Never ever lose that confidence! that's the foundation of your dreams✨
